Ibu pun juga begitu.

707
00:56:10,605 --> 00:56:12,752
Kau pun selalu ada, saat
Ibu makan daging babi goreng.

708
00:56:12,752 --> 00:56:14,726
Saat Ibu membuka mata pagi hari.

709
00:56:14,726 --> 00:56:16,947
Saat Ibu melihat kereta melaju.

710
00:56:16,947 --> 00:56:19,458
Setiap saat.

711
00:56:20,246 --> 00:56:21,964
Tapi Ibu...

712
00:56:23,772 --> 00:56:25,255
Itu semua...

713
00:56:25,255 --> 00:56:28,377
...kita tidak benar-benar bersama.

714
00:56:30,679 --> 00:56:31,873
Itu...

715
00:56:33,045 --> 00:56:35,310
...cuma bohong.

716
00:56:41,121 --> 00:56:42,755
Kau benar, Yoon Bok.

717
00:56:44,793 --> 00:56:46,824
Ini kebohongan, tapi...

718
00:56:48,732 --> 00:56:50,996
...tapi kita pandai berbohong.

719
00:56:52,406 --> 00:56:55,286
Sama seperti halnya kau
memikirkan hal-hal yang kau sukai...

720
00:56:56,601 --> 00:56:58,797
