725
00:57:21,596 --> 00:57:23,000
Suatu hari...

726
00:57:26,246 --> 00:57:28,250
...kita pasti bertemu lagi.

727
00:57:30,478 --> 00:57:33,623
Sama seperti halnya Ibu
dan Nenek Jari bisa bertemu lagi.

728
00:58:42,639 --> 00:58:44,261
Nenek?

729
00:58:53,081 --> 00:58:54,476
Yoon Bok?

730
00:58:54,862 --> 00:58:56,728
Nenek baik-baik saja?

731
00:59:00,018 --> 00:59:01,677
Sungguh kau Yoon Bok?

732
00:59:01,677 --> 00:59:02,813
Ya.

733
00:59:03,958 --> 00:59:05,884
Apa aku sudah mati?

734
00:59:07,156 --> 00:59:08,982
Kau bukan hantu, 'kan?

735
00:59:10,085 --> 00:59:11,857
Aku bukan hantu.

736
00:59:11,857 --> 00:59:13,565
Aku naik kereta api kesini.

737
00:59:16,065 --> 00:59:17,293
Begitu, ya.

738
00:59:19,096 --> 00:59:20,940
Mau kupanggilkan Ibu?

739
